<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Further_reading">Further reading</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=OpenGL&amp;action=edit&amp;section=28" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Dave Shreiner, The Khronos OpenGL ARB Working Group: <i>OpenGL Programming Guide: The Official Guide to Learning OpenGL, Version 4.3 (8th Edition)</i>, Addison-Wesley, March 30, 2013, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780321773036" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-321-77303-6</a></li>
<li>Graham Sellers, Richard S. Wright, Nicholas Haemel: <i>OpenGL SuperBible: Comprehensive Tutorial and Reference (6th Edition)</i>, Addison-Wesley, July 31, 2013, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780321902948" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-321-90294-8</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rost,_Randi_J." title="Rost, Randi J." class="mw-redirect">Rost, Randi J.</a>: <i>OpenGL Shading Language (3rd Edition)</i>, Addison-Wesley, July 30, 2009, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780321637635" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-321-63763-5</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eric_Lengyel" title="Eric Lengyel">Lengyel, Eric</a>: <i>The OpenGL Extensions Guide</i>, Charles River Media, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/1584502940" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 1-58450-294-0</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenGL_Architecture_Review_Board" title="OpenGL Architecture Review Board">OpenGL Architecture Review Board</a>, et al.: <i>OpenGL Reference Manual: The Official Reference Document to OpenGL, Version 1.4</i>, Addison-Wesley, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/032117383X" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-321-17383-X</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenGL_Architecture_Review_Board" title="OpenGL Architecture Review Board">OpenGL Architecture Review Board</a>, et al.: <i>OpenGL Programming Guide: The Official Guide to Learning OpenGL, Version 2, Fifth Edition</i>, Addison-Wesley, <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/0321335732" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-321-33573-2</a></li>
</ul>
